{"tid":1802611,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎2020, 有少少抗爭既前瞻意見","createTime":"2019-12-29T15:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T15:42:56.000Z","uid":196536,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1fcc44d4d840394931cd7ed87f6278ebc0701b","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"2019就黎完<br />\n2020又係打仗既一年<br />\n面對極權 我地唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過新一年我地要keep住個momentum 早著先機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有D準備工夫我地要開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為2020會有以下事件發生:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>立法會選舉</strong></span><br />\n<em>敵人: 港共政府 保皇黨 黑警</em><br />\n呢個已經好多手足搶佔緊功能界別灘頭, 另外新一屆區議會議員亦會履新, 佢地一定要落區做多D公民教育, 喚醒更多人既公民意識!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新年, 端午節, 中秋節等中式節日</strong></span><br />\n<em>敵人: 藍店</em><br />\n冇錯, 每年都有咁講黎做咩? 因為我要講既係黃色經濟圈個準備工夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019既中秋 有部份黃色餅店搶佔左唔少月餅市場 例如四喜 聖羅蘭(?) 仲有其他小店<br />\n不過好明顯唔夠威脅我地主要敵人美心!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日開始見到手足發覺新年個戰場我地準備不足 開左po警醒 不過恐怕已經趕唔切攻佔新年糕點市場 美心可能可以用呢個機會回氣 悲報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過錯唔緊要最緊要改! 龍頭黃店 區議員 政黨 著名KOL/youtuber 都可以帶頭搵工場整糕點賣<br />\n之後既端午, 中秋, 繼續做, 有利可圖之下必定可以壯大黃金經濟圈!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>奧運</strong></span><br />\n<em>敵人: TVB 支那運動員 </em><br />\n我地一定要報道(或盡可能報道) 所有香港運動員既動向 就算係幾唔出名 幾唔入流 都起碼要有直播串流跟進佢地既比賽情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡可能搵方法可以好似反送中直播台咁 香港人可以好易搵到直播 呢個係對香港運動員既實在支持 千萬唔可以忽略! 另外盡可能多D佢地戰果既報道 (如果該運動員係藍就算啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有D國際大事羅列如下<br />\n台灣選舉<br />\n英國脫歐<br />\n杜拜世博: 另一個大型國際event, 可能要靠國際戰線手足幫手<br />\n美國總統選舉<br />\n<br />\n手足一齊集思廣益 歡迎討論下應該點做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">黑警死全家</div></span>"},{"pid":"8c40c49866b3d196c119095b1722338d3cb3d5ab","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc54cb145f47eb500b1b3f2dbfe16e0ebff5e3aa","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:34:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2243d98d08a4b43113213f39a5ecc9b849631cf3","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c418552b1e2ec1bb8fb512c1a46e0e96db9e50e4","tid":1802611,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c40c49866b3d196c119095b1722338d3cb3d5ab","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:53:46.000Z","msg":"開過 la <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我 P-牌 推 五 yuk"},{"pid":"026ec0e2b27b8d150c9b9aba87e03db56e659c49","tid":1802611,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c418552b1e2ec1bb8fb512c1a46e0e96db9e50e4","tid":1802611,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c40c49866b3d196c119095b